&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://example.com/posts/scraping-sina-esg-grades/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (1 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Jupyter-notebook</category><category>Python</category><category>Selenium</category><category>爬虫</category><guid>https://example.com/posts/scraping-sina-esg-grades/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 12 Jan 2023 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Plotting with pandas</title><link>https://example.com/posts/plotting-with-pandas/</link><dc:creator>Tom</dc:creator><description>&lt;div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"&gt;&lt;div class="prompt input_prompt"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="inner_cell"&gt;
&lt;div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在数据分析过程中，我们常常碰到需要快速绘图的场景。比如，在回归分析前看一下 y 和 x 的散点图。对于这类需求，pandas 提供了一个 &lt;a href="https://pandas.pydata.org/docs/reference/api/pandas.DataFrame.plot.html"&gt;&lt;code&gt;pandas.DataFrame.plot&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 方法可以方便快捷地实现可视化。&lt;code&gt;pandas.DataFrame.plot&lt;/code&gt; 方法是对 &lt;code&gt;matplotlib.axes.Axes.plot&lt;/code&gt; 的封装，所以在调用该方法前，我们需要导入 matplotlib 包。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://example.com/posts/plotting-with-pandas/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (4 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Jupyter-notebook</category><category>Pandas</category><category>数据可视化</category><guid>https://example.com/posts/plotting-with-pandas/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 01 May 2022 19:52:05 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>